#: src/container/compose.md:1
msgid "Compose Orchestration (`perry/compose`)"
msgstr "Compose オーケストレーション（`perry/compose`）"

#: src/container/compose.md:3
msgid ""
"`perry/compose` brings the `docker compose up / down / ps / exec / logs` "
"workflow into TypeScript. The spec is a TS object literal that mirrors the "
"[Compose Specification](https://github.com/compose-spec/compose-"
"spec/blob/main/schema/compose-spec.json), the engine is in-process Rust (no "
"shell-out to a `docker-compose` binary), and dependency ordering / rollback "
"/ interpolation all run natively."
msgstr ""
"`perry/compose` は `docker compose up / down / ps / exec / logs` のワークフローを "
"TypeScript に取り込みます。仕様は [Compose 仕様](https://github.com/compose-spec/compose-"
"spec/blob/main/schema/compose-spec.json) を反映した TS "
"オブジェクトリテラルで記述し、エンジンはインプロセスの Rust（`docker-compose` "
"バイナリへのシェルアウトなし）で実装されており、依存順序解決・ロールバック・補間はすべてネイティブに動作します。"

#: src/container/compose.md:10
msgid "Bringing up a single-service stack"
msgstr "単一サービススタックの起動"

#: src/container/compose.md:41
msgid ""
"The handle returned from `up()` is an opaque integer (NaN-boxed with "
"`POINTER_TAG`); pass it as the first argument to [`down`](#tearing-down) / "
"[`ps`](#status--logs--exec) / [`logs`](#status--logs--exec) / "
"[`exec`](#status--logs--exec). The template-string interpolation `${stack}` "
"renders as `[object Object]` because of the NaN-boxing tag; coerce "
"explicitly with `String(stack)` if you need to log it."
msgstr ""
"`up()` から返されるハンドルは不透明な整数（`POINTER_TAG` で NaN ボックス化）です。これを [`down`](#tearing-"
"down) / [`ps`](#status--logs--exec) / [`logs`](#status--logs--exec) / "
"[`exec`](#status--logs--exec) の最初の引数として渡してください。テンプレート文字列補間 `${stack}` は NaN "
"ボックス化タグのため `[object Object]` としてレンダリングされます。ログに出力する必要がある場合は `String(stack)` "
"で明示的に変換してください。"

#: src/container/compose.md:49
msgid "Multi-service stack with healthcheck-gated startup"
msgstr "ヘルスチェックゲート付き起動を使用したマルチサービススタック"

#: src/container/compose.md:51
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { up as upMulti } from \"perry/compose\";\n"
"\n"
"async function bringUpMultiServiceStack(): Promise<void> {\n"
"    // depends_on with `condition: 'service_healthy'` blocks the\n"
"    // dependent service until the dependency's healthcheck reports\n"
"    // healthy. Use the map form (not the bare-array form) to pass\n"
"    // the condition.\n"
"    await upMulti({\n"
"        version: \"3.8\",\n"
"        services: {\n"
"            db: {\n"
"                image: \"postgres:16-alpine\",\n"
"                container_name: \"app-db\", // stable DNS target for siblings\n"
"                environment: {\n"
"                    POSTGRES_USER:     \"app\",\n"
"                    POSTGRES_PASSWORD: \"${APP_DB_PASSWORD:-changeme}\",\n"
"                    POSTGRES_DB:       \"app\",\n"
"                },\n"
"                volumes: [\"app-pgdata:/var/lib/postgresql/data\"],\n"
"                networks: [\"app-db-net\"],\n"
"                healthcheck: {\n"
"                    test: [\"CMD-SHELL\", \"pg_isready -U app -d app\"],\n"
"                    interval: \"5s\",\n"
"                    timeout: \"3s\",\n"
"                    retries: 10,\n"
"                    start_period: \"30s\",\n"
"                },\n"
"            },\n"
"            api: {\n"
"                image: \"myorg/api:1.0\",\n"
"                depends_on: { db: { condition: \"service_healthy\" } },\n"
"                environment: {\n"
"                    DATABASE_URL: \"postgres://app:changeme@app-db:5432/app\",\n"
"                },\n"
"                ports: [\"8080:8080\"],\n"
"                networks: [\"app-db-net\", \"app-web-net\"],\n"
"                restart: \"unless-stopped\",\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"        networks: {\n"
"            \"app-db-net\":  { driver: \"bridge\", internal: true }, // db unreachable from host\n"
"            \"app-web-net\": { driver: \"bridge\" },\n"
"        },\n"
"        volumes: {\n"
"            \"app-pgdata\": { driver: \"local\" },\n"
"        },\n"
"    });\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/compose.md:102
msgid "This pattern combines several production-grade primitives:"
msgstr "このパターンはいくつかのプロダクショングレードのプリミティブを組み合わせています:"

#: src/container/compose.md:104
msgid "Primitive"
msgstr "プリミティブ"

#: src/container/compose.md:106
msgid "`container_name: 'app-db'`"
msgstr "`container_name: 'app-db'`"

#: src/container/compose.md:106
msgid ""
"Forces a stable container name so docker's embedded DNS resolves `app-db` to"
" the postgres container's IP. **See the [DNS gotcha below](#cross-service-"
"dns-gotcha).**"
msgstr ""
"安定したコンテナ名を強制し、Dockerの組み込みDNSが `app-db` "
"をPostgresコンテナのIPに解決できるようにします。**[下記のDNSに関する注意点](#cross-service-dns-"
"gotcha)を参照してください。**"

#: src/container/compose.md:107
msgid "`healthcheck: { test: [...], interval, retries, start_period }`"
msgstr "`healthcheck: { test: [...], interval, retries, start_period }`"

#: src/container/compose.md:107
msgid ""
"Per-service liveness probe. Compose-spec § service.healthcheck shape — "
"Perry's engine honors it for `depends_on` gating."
msgstr ""
"サービスごとのliveness probe。Compose仕様 § service.healthcheck の形式 — Perryのエンジンは "
"`depends_on` のゲーティングのためにこれを利用します。"

#: src/container/compose.md:108
msgid "`depends_on: { db: { condition: 'service_healthy' } }`"
msgstr "`depends_on: { db: { condition: 'service_healthy' } }`"

#: src/container/compose.md:108
msgid ""
"Holds the dependent service back until the dependency reports healthy. Three"
" valid conditions: `service_started`, `service_healthy`, "
"`service_completed_successfully`."
msgstr ""
"依存サービスが healthy を報告するまで、依存側のサービスの起動を保留します。有効な条件は3つあります: "
"`service_started`、`service_healthy`、`service_completed_successfully`。"

#: src/container/compose.md:109
msgid "`networks: { ..., internal: true }`"
msgstr "`networks: { ..., internal: true }`"

#: src/container/compose.md:109
msgid ""
"Marks the network as internal-only — postgres is unreachable from the host "
"or from sibling stacks. See [Networking](./networking.md)."
msgstr ""
"ネットワークをinternal専用にマークします — "
"postgresはホストや兄弟スタックからアクセスできなくなります。[ネットワーキング](./networking.md)を参照してください。"

#: src/container/compose.md:110
msgid "`restart: 'unless-stopped'`"
msgstr "`restart: 'unless-stopped'`"

#: src/container/compose.md:110
msgid ""
"The runtime restarts the container after a crash, but not after an explicit "
"`docker stop`."
msgstr "runtimeはクラッシュ後にコンテナを再起動しますが、明示的な `docker stop` の後には再起動しません。"

#: src/container/compose.md:112
msgid ""
"The full `ComposeSpec` shape is exported from `perry/compose` as "
"`ComposeSpec`, with sub-types `Service`, `ComposeNetwork`, `ComposeVolume`, "
"`Build`, and `Healthcheck`."
msgstr ""
"完全な `ComposeSpec` の型は `perry/compose` から `ComposeSpec` "
"としてエクスポートされており、サブタイプとして "
"`Service`、`ComposeNetwork`、`ComposeVolume`、`Build`、`Healthcheck` があります。"

#: src/container/compose.md:116
msgid "Recognised Service fields"
msgstr "認識される Service フィールド"

#: src/container/compose.md:118
msgid ""
"The full set Perry's engine understands (matches compose-spec § services):"
msgstr "Perryのエンジンが理解するフィールドの完全なセットです（compose仕様 § services に準拠）:"

#: src/container/compose.md:120
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"interface Service {\n"
"  image?: string;\n"
"  container_name?: string;\n"
"  ports?: string[];                                              // \"host:container[:proto]\"\n"
"  environment?: Record<string, string> | string[];               // map or KEY=VALUE list\n"
"  labels?: Record<string, string>;\n"
"  volumes?: string[];                                            // \"host:container[:ro]\" or \"named:container\"\n"
"  build?: Build;                                                 // { context, dockerfile, args, … }\n"
"  depends_on?: string[] | Record<string, { condition?: string }>;\n"
"  restart?: \"no\" | \"always\" | \"on-failure\" | \"unless-stopped\";\n"
"  entrypoint?: string | string[];\n"
"  command?: string | string[];\n"
"  networks?: string[];\n"
"  healthcheck?: Healthcheck;\n"
"  user?: string;\n"
"  working_dir?: string;\n"
"  read_only?: boolean;\n"
"  privileged?: boolean;\n"
"  cap_add?: string[];\n"
"  cap_drop?: string[];\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/compose.md:144
msgid "`Healthcheck` shape"
msgstr "`Healthcheck` の形式"

#: src/container/compose.md:146
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"interface Healthcheck {\n"
"  test?: string[];           // [\"CMD\", \"<cmd>\", ...] | [\"CMD-SHELL\", \"<line>\"] | [\"NONE\"]\n"
"  interval?: string;         // Go duration: \"5s\", \"2m\", \"1h30m\"\n"
"  timeout?: string;\n"
"  retries?: number;\n"
"  start_period?: string;     // grace period before retries count\n"
"  disable?: boolean;\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/compose.md:157
msgid "Environment variable interpolation"
msgstr "環境変数の補間"

#: src/container/compose.md:159
msgid ""
"Compose's `${VAR}` and `${VAR:-default}` placeholders work in TS-side specs "
"too — Perry expands them against `process.env` at the FFI boundary, "
"**before** the JSON gets parsed:"
msgstr ""
"Composeの `${VAR}` および `${VAR:-default}` プレースホルダーはTSサイドの仕様でも動作します — "
"PerryはFFI境界で `process.env` に対してこれらを展開します。**JSONがパースされる前に**展開が行われます:"

#: src/container/compose.md:163
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { up as upEnv } from \"perry/compose\";\n"
"\n"
"// Compose YAML interpolation (`${VAR}` / `${VAR:-default}`) is applied\n"
"// to TS-side specs at the FFI boundary too — set `process.env` keys\n"
"// before calling up() and they'll resolve in the spec values.\n"
"async function envInterpolatedStack(): Promise<void> {\n"
"    await upEnv({\n"
"        version: \"3.8\",\n"
"        services: {\n"
"            web: {\n"
"                image: \"nginx:${NGINX_VERSION:-alpine}\",\n"
"                ports: [\"${WEB_PORT:-8080}:80\"],\n"
"                environment: {\n"
"                    SERVER_NAME: \"${WEB_DOMAIN:-localhost}\",\n"
"                },\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"    });\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

