#: src/container/compose.md:194 src/container/networking.md:65
msgid "Cross-service DNS"
msgstr "クロスサービスDNS"

#: src/container/compose.md:196
msgid ""
"Each service registers its **service key** (`db`, `api`, …) as a network "
"alias automatically — Perry's engine emits `--network-alias <key>` per "
"service per network on every `run`. So this just works:"
msgstr ""
"各サービスはその**サービスキー**（`db`、`api` など）をネットワークエイリアスとして自動的に登録します — Perryのエンジンはすべての "
"`run` において、サービスごとにネットワークごとに `--network-alias <key>` "
"を出力します。そのため、以下はそのまま動作します:"

#: src/container/compose.md:201
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"api: {\n"
"  image: \"myapp/api\",\n"
"  environment: {\n"
"    // ✅ \"db\" resolves in DNS via the auto-registered service-key alias\n"
"    DATABASE_URL: \"postgres://user:pw@db:5432/app\",\n"
"  },\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/compose.md:211
msgid ""
"`container_name` is no longer required for cross-service DNS. You can still "
"set one if you want a stable name visible to `docker ps`, but the service "
"key alone is enough for in-network resolution. Pre-v0.5.372 docs described a"
" workaround using `container_name` pinning — that pattern still works but is"
" now optional."
msgstr ""
"`container_name` はクロスサービスDNSに必須ではなくなりました。`docker ps` "
"で確認できる安定した名前が必要な場合は引き続き設定できますが、ネットワーク内での名前解決にはサービスキーだけで十分です。v0.5.372以前のドキュメントでは"
" `container_name` のピン留めを使ったワークアラウンドが説明されていましたが、そのパターンは引き続き動作しますが、現在はオプションです。"

#: src/container/compose.md:217
msgid "Tearing down"
msgstr "停止と削除"

#: src/container/compose.md:234
msgid ""
"`down(handle)` removes containers and networks, and **preserves named "
"volumes by default**. Pass `{ volumes: true }` to also drop the volumes "
"(destroys committed data — use only for \"rip and replace\" redeploy or test"
" cleanup)."
msgstr ""
"`down(handle)` はコンテナとネットワークを削除し、**デフォルトでは名前付きボリュームを保持します**。ボリュームも削除するには `{ "
"volumes: true }` を渡してください（コミット済みデータが破壊されます — "
"「完全置換」の再デプロイやテストのクリーンアップ時のみ使用してください）。"

#: src/container/compose.md:239
msgid "`down` option"
msgstr "`down` オプション"

#: src/container/compose.md:241
msgid "Also remove named volumes after containers + networks."
msgstr "コンテナとネットワークの削除後に名前付きボリュームも削除します。"

#: src/container/compose.md:242
msgid "`removeOrphans`"
msgstr "`removeOrphans`"

#: src/container/compose.md:242
msgid ""
"Remove containers labelled with this stack's project but not in the current "
"spec."
msgstr "このスタックのプロジェクトのラベルが付いているが、現在の仕様には含まれていないコンテナを削除します。"

#: src/container/compose.md:244
msgid "Status / logs / exec"
msgstr "ステータス / ログ / exec"

#: src/container/compose.md:246
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import {\n"
"    ps,\n"
"    logs as composeLogs,\n"
"    exec as composeExec,\n"
"    config,\n"
"    start,\n"
"    stop,\n"
"    restart,\n"
"} from \"perry/compose\";\n"
"\n"
"async function manageStack(stack: number): Promise<void> {\n"
"    // Status of every service in the stack (returns a registry\n"
"    // handle to a ContainerInfo[]; user-side array materialisation\n"
"    // is a follow-up ergonomics task).\n"
"    const statusHandle = await ps(stack);\n"
"    console.log(statusHandle);\n"
"\n"
"    // Aggregated logs from one or all services.\n"
"    await composeLogs(stack, { service: \"db\", tail: 200 });\n"
"\n"
"    // Exec a command inside a service's container by service KEY\n"
"    // (not container name) — the engine resolves the service to its\n"
"    // running container internally.\n"
"    await composeExec(stack, \"db\", [\"pg_isready\"]);\n"
"\n"
"    // Resolved YAML the engine actually used (post-interpolation).\n"
"    const yaml = await config(stack);\n"
"    console.log(yaml);\n"
"\n"
"    // Stop / start / restart by service key. `services: []` (or\n"
"    // omitted) targets every service in the stack.\n"
"    await stop(stack, [\"api\"]);\n"
"    await start(stack, [\"api\"]);\n"
"    await restart(stack, []);\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/compose.md:284
msgid ""
"Like `perry/container.{logs, exec}`, the compose `logs` and `exec` return "
"registry-id handles for the `ContainerLogs` array. Treat them as opaque for "
"now; user-side materialisation is a planned ergonomics task."
msgstr ""
"`perry/container.{logs, exec}` と同様に、compose の `logs` および `exec` は "
"`ContainerLogs` "
"配列のレジストリIDハンドルを返します。現時点ではこれらを不透明な値として扱ってください。ユーザー側でのマテリアライズは今後のエルゴノミクス改善として予定されています。"

