"`NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription` in `Info.plist`. Backed by "
"`CLLocationManager`."
msgstr ""
"`Info.plist`内の`NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription`。`CLLocationManager`によってサポートされます。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:64
